Was in town for the Rolling Stones tour opener. Got a notification that Parmalee wasn't playing and the start time was pushed back so I went to the Shidoobee party at Henke & Pilot about a mile away and stayed for 20 minutes and said hello to Doug and a few other people before walking to the arena ticketless. Took a good 30 minutes until a Vet Tix beneficiary handed me a ticket. If you have tickets you can't use I would recommend donating, I have done that in the past though I no longer buy advance tickets to almost anything anymore.
